Here's the Terraform code that creates an EC2 instance of g4dn.xlarge type with 100GB root disk size in the eu-central-1 region:

```
provider aws {
  region = eu-central-1
}

resource aws_instance my_instance {
  ami           = ami-0808d0e720f26ccc2
  instance_type = g4dn.xlarge

  root_block_device {
    volume_size = 100
  }

  tags = {
    Name = My EC2 Instance
  }
}
```
